caption:
NYC: Run Strong community runs are back! Join us every Friday beginning October 18th at 7:00am at Pier 46 for a team workout to start your day.  New to Run Strong? It’s our take on running, centered around hybrid athletes who blend strength & endurance. No equipment necessary - all you have to do is show up.

Can’t make it this week? No sweat - we’ll be at Pier 46 every Friday unless we say otherwise. Stay tuned to our broadcast channel for regular updates.

When: Friday, 7:00am
Where: Pier 46 (West Side Path)
 Dynamic Warm-Up (6:50am start) 3-4 Miles (out & back)
w/ burpees, squats, or push-ups every ~1km
 #betterthanyesterday #runstrong
